<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 - 頁面未找到</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #74ebd5, #acb6e5);
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 3rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        max-width: 500px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 6rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #e74c3c;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        background: #3498db;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      a:hover {
        background: #2980b9;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .illustration {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 300px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img src="/images/404-illustration.png" alt="404 錯誤插圖" class="illustration" />
      <h1>404</h1>
      <p>抱歉，我們找不到您要的頁面。<br />請確認網址是否正確。</p>
      <a href="/">返回首頁</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
